      "span_text": "London and (ii) to compare the efficiency of SANGRA in predicting South Asian ethnicity of the UKRR data to the published validation results.  We also assessed whether prediction of ethnicity by SANGRA led to a change in South Asian patients' baseline characteristics by testing"
